This is a sample code to show how to use python client of sofa-pbrpc.

Guide
=====

1) Install the python library for protobuf.

     $ cd ${PROTOBUF_SOURCE_DIR}/python
     $ python setup.py install

2) Install the python client library for sofa-pbrpc.

     $ cd ..
     $ python setup.py install

3) Generate `echo_service_pb2.py'.

     $ sh compile_proto.sh

4) Start the rpc server.

     $ cd ../../sample/echo
     $ make
     $ ./server

5) Run the python client.

     $ python client_sample.py

